display="inline"><![CDATA[g]]></fr:tex>. Now by transitivity, <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[T]]></fr:tex> covers <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[x]]></fr:tex>, so that by stability, <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[T]]></fr:tex>
    covers <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex>.</fr:li></fr:ul>
